      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so you can count on it for all your upcoming adventures. It runs smoothly and looks great inside and out\u2014perfect if you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s been cared for. I've loved every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
