    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six heritage. The powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, paired with a tactile ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on performance, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system to ensure variable valve timing remains within factory tolerances. While the exterior displays honest patina from spirited driving, the suspension bushings are tight and the compression across all six cylinders is consistent. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for mechanical longevity and cornering precision.",
      "price": 36500.0,
